                    "body": "This same error is appearing in release 1.7.6, with a different scenario. \nex.\npublic function getusers(); \/\/ throws \"Uncaught exception 'Zend_Server_Reflection_Exception'\"\n\npublic function getusers($userid); \/\/ does not throw error\n\nprivate function getusers(); \/\/ does not throw error\n\nError is only thrown when function is declared public with no parameters.\n\nEnvironment:\nMac 10.5.6\nXAMPP for Mac OS X 0.7.4  ",
